Welcome back to The Best & The Brightest. I=E2=80=99m Leigh Ann
Caldwell, driving the sled on this snowy day in Washington.

=C2=A0

As a matter of fact, there=E2=80=99s a veritable snowball fight ramping up =
on the Hill, where the Senate Budget Committee spent the day marking up its=
 two-step reconciliation process, and giving a big middle finger to the Hou=
se for its lackadaisical pace in pushing forward Trump=E2=80=99s agenda. In=
deed, the Senate=E2=80=99s $340 billion outline for a border
security and defense funding bill=E2=80=94the first step in a reconciliatio=
